<div class="mdui-typo"><h1 id="forever-adv">forever <strong><em>adv</em></strong></h1>
<p>英 /fər'evə(r)/    美 /fər'evər/  </p>
<h2 id="_1">释义</h2>
<h4 id="1-for-ever">1.★ <strong>永远；老是 (for ever)：</strong></h4>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>Nobody lives forever. 
没有人会永生。</p></div>

<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>She is forever talking. 
她总是喋喋不休。</p></div></div>